    // kind of factory
    // - e.g. a customized TInterfaceStub/TInterfaceMock, a TServiceContainer,
    // a TDDDRepositoryRestObjectMapping or any factory class
    // - by default, only TInterfaceStub/TInterfaceMock will be owned by this
